Package com.message.security

Class Utility

java.lang.Object
com.message.security.Utility
public final class Utility extends Object
The Utility class contains several methods and a couple of class fields. It cannot be instantiated. This class helps the Encrypt and Decrypt class of com.message.security class. All the core encrypting and decrypting operation methods are defined in this class. Set the keypair using setKeyPair(int, int) before using this class and do not forget to call resetKeyPair() after finishing.
Author:
tinykishore
